<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<addon id="game.libretro.retro8"
		name="PICO-8 (Retro8)"
		version="0.1.0.25"
		provider-name="jakz">
	<requires>
		<import addon="game.libretro" version="1.0.0"/>
		<import addon="game.controller.default" version="1.0.0"/>
	</requires>
	<extension point="kodi.gameclient"
			library_@PLATFORM@="@LIBRARY_FILENAME@">
		<platforms></platforms>
		<extensions>p8</extensions>
		<supports_vfs>true</supports_vfs>
		<supports_standalone>false</supports_standalone>
		<requires_opengl>false</requires_opengl>
	</extension>
	<extension point="xbmc.addon.metadata">
		<license>GPLv3</license>
		<platform>@PLATFORM@</platform>
		<source>https://github.com/kodi-game/game.libretro.retro8</source>
		<assets>
			<icon>resources/icon.png</icon>
			<screenshot>resources/screenshot-01.jpg</screenshot>
			<screenshot>resources/screenshot-02.jpg</screenshot>
			<screenshot>resources/screenshot-03.jpg</screenshot>
		</assets>
		<summary lang="da_DK">PICO-8 (Retro8)</summary>
		<summary lang="en_GB">PICO-8 (Retro8)</summary>
		<summary lang="es_ES">PICO-8 (Retro8)</summary>
		<summary lang="ko_KR">피코-8 (레트로8)</summary>
		<summary lang="zh_CN">PICO-8 (Retro8)</summary>
		<description lang="da_DK">Retro8 er en open source-implementering af PICO-8 Fantasy Console.[CR][CR]Meget af PICO-8 API&apos;en fungerer med god ydeevne, inklusive grundlæggende lyd og musik, selvom den stadig mangler nogle obskure Lua-udvidelses-quirks og fast aritmetisk understøttelse.</description>
		<description lang="de_DE">Retro8 ist eine Open-Source-Implementierung der PICO-8-Fantasy-Konsole.[CR][CR]Ein Großteil der PICO-8-API funktioniert mit guter Performance, einschließlich grundlegender Sound- und Musikfunktionen, allerdings fehlen noch einige obskure Lua-Erweiterungen und feste arithmetische Unterstützung.</description>
		<description lang="en_GB">Retro8 is an open source implementation of the PICO-8 Fantasy Console.[CR][CR]Much of the PICO-8 API is working with good performance, including basic sound and music, though it is still missing some obscure Lua extension quirks and fixed arithmetic support.</description>
		<description lang="es_ES">Retro8 es una implementación de código abierto de la Consola de Fantasía PICO-8.[CR][CR]Gran parte de la API de PICO-8 está funcionando con buen rendimiento, incluyendo sonido básico y música, aunque todavía le faltan algunas peculiaridades oscuras de la extensión Lua y soporte aritmético fijo.</description>
		<description lang="ko_KR">Retro8은 PICO-8 Fantasy Console의 오픈 소스 구현입니다.[CR][CR]PICO-8 API의 많은 부분이 기본 사운드와 음악을 포함하여 좋은 성능으로 동작하고 있지만, 아직 몇 가지 애매한 Lua 확장 기능과 고정 산술 지원이 누락되어 있습니다.</description>
		<description lang="zh_CN">Retro8 是 PICO-8 Fantasy 主机的开源实现。[CR][CR]PICO-8 API 的大部分性能都很好，包括基本的声音和音乐，尽管它仍然缺少一些模糊的 Lua extension quirks 和定点计算支持。</description>
	</extension>
</addon>
